		<title><sourcexml>table[@pgwide]</sourcexml> check attribute value <lnpid>id-UK01-39207</lnpid></title>
		<body>
			<section>
				<p>This is a rule specific for all UK Streams regarding
					<sourcexml>table[@pgwide]</sourcexml>.</p>
				<p><sourcexml>table</sourcexml> converts as described in <xref
					href="../common_newest/Rosetta_table-LxAdv-table.dita"
					>"<sourcexml>table</sourcexml> to <targetxml>table</targetxml>
					(id-CCCC-10475)"</xref>.</p>
				<p><ul>
					<li>If <sourcexml>@pgwide</sourcexml> value is <sourcexml>"0"</sourcexml> (zero)
						then it becomes <targetxml>@pgwide="0"</targetxml> and if value is anything
						else then it set to default value <targetxml>@pgwide="1"</targetxml>.</li>
					<li>If the <sourcexml>@pgwide</sourcexml> attribute is missing inside source
						(rosetta) document then it should be suppressed in NL target output.</li>
				</ul></p>
				<pre>
        <b>EXAMPLE 1: Source attribute value "zero" - <sourcexml>@pgwide="0"</sourcexml></b>
            
<b><i>Source XML</i></b>
<![CDATA[
<table frame="none" pgwide="0">
    <!-- contents of table -->
</table>

<table frame="none" pgwide="1">
    <!-- contents of table -->
</table>
]]> 
<b><i>Target XML</i></b>
<![CDATA[
<table frame="none" pgwide="0">
    <!-- contents of table -->
</table>

<table frame="none" pgwide="1">
    <!-- contents of table -->
</table>
]]>
                </pre>
				<pre>
        <b>EXAMPLE 2: If <sourcexml>@pgwide</sourcexml> attribute is any other value then it should be default value <targetxml>@pgwide="1"</targetxml></b>
            
<b><i>Source XML</i></b>
<![CDATA[
<table frame="none" pgwide="true">
    <!-- contents of table -->
</table>
]]> 
<b><i>Target XML</i></b>
<![CDATA[
<table frame="none" pgwide="1">
    <!-- contents of table -->
</table>
]]>
                </pre>
				<pre>
        <b>EXAMPLE 2: <sourcexml>@pgwide</sourcexml> is missing in source then suppress in NL target</b>
            
<b><i>Source XML</i></b>
<![CDATA[
<table frame="none">
    <!-- contents of table -->
</table>
]]> 
<b><i>Target XML</i></b>
<![CDATA[
<table frame="none">
    <!-- contents of table -->
</table>
]]>
                </pre>
			</section>
